    12→ *
    13→ * <p>This interface is agnostic of any delivery mechanism (REST, GraphQL, CLI, etc.)
    14→ * and must be implemented by the application service residing in the domain/service
    15→ * layer. Outbound dependencies (payment gateway, inventory service, etc.) must be
    16→ * injected into that service via secondary ports.</p>
