    51→    /**
    52→     * Places a new order, performs stock reservation and attempts immediate payment capture.
    53→     *
    54→     * @param command checkout information supplied by the client
    55→     * @param customerId ID of the user placing the order
    56→     * @return the newly created Order aggregate, reflecting the persisted state
